      "id": 402,
      "sender_id": 97,
      "content": "<p>Hello!</p>\n<p>I would like to report an issue with the <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/datasets/SAIRfoundation/equational-theories-selected-problems/blob/main/data/hard.jsonl\">Hard dataset</a>: only 69 out of 200 entries form unique <code>(equation1, equation2)</code> pairs.</p>\n<p>Here are a few dupe examples (<a href=\"/user_uploads/5/c7/jglNSkwuY-W5aFFJbwylvOoq/hard_problems_unique_pairs.txt\">see full list file, one row per unique equation pair</a>):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>hard_0024, hard_0076, hard_0128, hard_0180</li>\n<li>hard_0047, hard_0099, hard_0151</li>\n<li>hard_0060, hard_0112, hard_0164</li>\n<li>hard_0020, hard_0072, hard_0124, hard_0176</li>\n<li>hard_0031, hard_0083, hard_0135, hard_0187</li>\n</ul>\n<p>NB: no such finding for the \"Normal\" dataset</p>",
