      "id": 541,
      "sender_id": 25,
      "content": "<p>We have uploaded two new public problem subsets to Hugging Face:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>hard2 is now available as a new 200-problem subset. It contains 100 problems with ground-truth TRUE labels and 100 problems with ground-truth FALSE labels.<br>\n  Link: <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/datasets/SAIRfoundation/equational-theories-selected-problems/viewer/hard2/train\">https://huggingface.co/datasets/SAIRfoundation/equational-theories-selected-problems/viewer/hard2/train</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>hard1 is also now available as the deduplicated version of the previous hard subset. It contains 69 problems total, with 24 ground-truth TRUE labels and 45 ground-truth FALSE labels.<br>\n  Link: <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/datasets/SAIRfoundation/equational-theories-selected-problems/viewer/hard1/train\">https://huggingface.co/datasets/SAIRfoundation/equational-theories-selected-problems/viewer/hard1/train</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Both subsets are now publicly available.</p>\n<p>Thanks to <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"97\">@Baptiste Polchlopek</span>  for pointing out the issue.</p>",
